### 게시글 추가
POST localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "category": "RESTAURANT",
  "title": "게시글 제목입니다",
  "hashtagName": ["해시태그5", "해시태그6"],
  "content": "게시글 내용입니다",
  "locationId": 13
}

### 코멘트 추가
@articleId=8
POST localhost:8080/api/articles/{{articleId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 5,
  "article_id": {{articleId}},
  "content": "댓글 내용입니다12345"
}


### 코멘트 조회
GET localhost:8080/api/articles/{{articleId}}/comments


### 코멘트 조회 (코멘트만)
GET localhost:8080/api/articles/{{articleId}}/commentsonly


### 코멘트 수정
@commentId = 3
PUT localhost:8080/api/comments/{{commentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "수정한 댓글입니다200"
}

### 코멘트 삭제
DELETE localhost:8080/api/comments/{{commentId}}


